tatami.core.agent.parametric

Enum AgentParameterName

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AgentParameterName>
      • tatami.core.agent.parametric.AgentParameterName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AgentParameterName>

    public enum AgentParameterName
extends java.lang.Enum<AgentParameterName>
    Here be all names of 'registered' parameters (see AgentParameters) used by any component of the agent.

    Each parameter has an internal name - the constant in the enum - and the name in the scenario file - given in the constructor of the enum constant.

    It would be advised that these values be used when reading from the XML file.

    Note about the javadoc: some links were not included in order to avoid imports outside of the core package.

    Author:
    Andrei Olaru
